WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Download the .dmg file from the web Dropbox folder that has been shared with you.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Double-click on the .dmg file and drag and drop the 'centrethird-scout' icon into you Applications folder.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.000
After installation, the centrethird-scout app will be available in your Applications.

